10N.F.summary: Enter Air Sp. z o.o. operates as a charter airline company in Poland. The company offers passenger air transportation services to various holiday destinations, including Egypt, Greece, Turkey, Tunisia, and Spain. It operates a fleet of 19 Boeing 737-800 aircraft and 2 B737 MAX 8 aircraft. The company was founded in 2009 and is based in Warsaw, Poland. Enter Air Sp. z o.o. is a subsidiary of Enter Air S.A.
